          ],
          "subtype": "sidebar",
          "text": "A valkyrie tempest often rides into battle on the backs of pegasi or other flying mounts. In such a case, the valkyrie tempest troop gains the following ability.   \n**Mounted Troop** Effects that target only animals or only humanoids may not work on the valkyrie tempest, subject to the GM's discretion.",
          "type": "section"
        }
      ],
      "sources": [
        {
          "link": {
            "alt": "Prey for Death pg. 119",
            "aonid": 231,
            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "Prey for Death pg. 119",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Prey for Death",
          "page": 119,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "While valkyries tend to travel alone or in small groups of two or three, they won't hesitate to rely on the old adage of \u201cstrength in numbers.\u201d",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
