            ],
            "effect": "The tempest attacks with their electrified spears, targeting all adjacent enemies (DC 38 basic Reflex save). The damage depends on the number of actions.  \n [#] 1d6+10 piercing damage plus 1d12 electricity  \n [##] 2d6+10 piercing damage plus 2d12 electricity  \n [###] 3d6+10 piercing damage plus 3d12 electricity",
            "frequency": "once per round",
            "links": [
